title: The Best Of Communism - Political & Revolutionary Songs (FLA
description:
The Best Of Communism

MP3/320

This is a collection of Communist political and revolutionary songs.

2. The Voice Of Lenin

3. Lenin-Song

5. The Partisans Of The Amur River

6. The Red Csepel Works

8. Polyushka

9. Soar Ahead, You Glorious Song

10. The Song Of The Republic

11. We Thank You, Comrade Rakosi

12. The Workers' Guards' March

13. Riflesong

14. On The Edge Of The Woods

15. Forward Together With The Party And The People

16. The KISZ Welds Us Into Unity

17. The DIVSZ March

18. Onward Youth, For Socialism

19. The Happy Pioneer (A Climbing Squirrel In Cheer/So Joyful Is The Pioneer...)

20. The Song Of Liberation

21. A Welcome To May

22. Let Our Song Ring Out Reolute/From Lips Fresh With Fortitude-Medley

23. The National Anthem Of The Soviet Union

24. The Anthem Of Communism


All MP3 tracks have ID3 tags for Album, Artist, Track Titles, and order in the album.  Some other information, such as Year, Genre, and Publisher may have been added if the information was available to me.

FLAC cannot be encoded by my software in a usable fashion with tags, so you must add them yourself. 

All albums will have album art included if it was available to me.

All MP3 files that I upload are encoded at TRUE 320 kbps.

All FLAC files that I upload are encoded at highest quality.  If the files seem a little large, that is why.
